  "detailed_description": "A string of disappearances has lead a novice detective to the village of Drakehorn.  Find out what's causing the disappearances before time runs out!  You're the only one strong enough (or foolish enough) to attempt such a feat.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/738190/extras/ada33d30a15cbcf927a8f82be907ef29.poster.avif?t=1634061963\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/738190/extras/ada33d30a15cbcf927a8f82be907ef29.webm?t=1634061963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/738190/extras/ada33d30a15cbcf927a8f82be907ef29.poster.avif?t=1634061963\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/738190/extras/ada33d30a15cbcf927a8f82be907ef29.webm?t=1634061963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>This is a short game where your choices will help or hinder your ability to solve the mystery!<br><br>No playthrough is exactly the same with Morth's skill check system.  Your choices will slightly increase certain skills and will help you overcome challenges.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/738190/extras/44065bf9d5c03d6ba3d607c41d5591d9.avif?t=1634061963\" width=800 height=222 /></span><br><br>The game will take approximately 15 minutes to complete with two possible endings and multiple playthroughs may be required to accomplish the desired ending.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/738190/extras/b9aad7f6cebbee4fbfdaaa7e325c53c1.avif?t=1634061963\" width=460 height=214 /></span><br><br><strong>features</strong><br><br>*Classic choose-your-own-adventure gameplay <br>*Chiptune Soundtrack <br>*Skill-check systems allows for varied gameplay<br>*Solve a Medieval Mystery!",
  "about_the_game": "A string of disappearances has lead a novice detective to the village of Drakehorn.  Find out what's causing the disappearances before time runs out!  You're the only one strong enough (or foolish enough) to attempt such a feat.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/738190/extras/ada33d30a15cbcf927a8f82be907ef29.poster.avif?t=1634061963\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/738190/extras/ada33d30a15cbcf927a8f82be907ef29.webm?t=1634061963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/738190/extras/ada33d30a15cbcf927a8f82be907ef29.poster.avif?t=1634061963\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/738190/extras/ada33d30a15cbcf927a8f82be907ef29.webm?t=1634061963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>This is a short game where your choices will help or hinder your ability to solve the mystery!<br><br>No playthrough is exactly the same with Morth's skill check system.  Your choices will slightly increase certain skills and will help you overcome challenges.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/738190/extras/44065bf9d5c03d6ba3d607c41d5591d9.avif?t=1634061963\" width=800 height=222 /></span><br><br>The game will take approximately 15 minutes to complete with two possible endings and multiple playthroughs may be required to accomplish the desired ending.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/738190/extras/b9aad7f6cebbee4fbfdaaa7e325c53c1.avif?t=1634061963\" width=460 height=214 /></span><br><br><strong>features</strong><br><br>*Classic choose-your-own-adventure gameplay <br>*Chiptune Soundtrack <br>*Skill-check systems allows for varied gameplay<br>*Solve a Medieval Mystery!",
